node.text:
Hydration • Taking you for a tour in the southeastern Aegean Sea. I am so happy to be back to one of my favourite places on earth, to share my moments into the wild nature, the rich heritage and the untouched beauty of #Karpathos island . First stop is Diakoftis beach, a small turquoise coloured gem of the island. W/ @visitkarpathosisland
#visitKarpathos #Greece
